  <img class="main-image" src="http://static.gossamer-threads.com/r3/images/masthead/plant.jpg" width="950" height="414" alt="Plant image" />
  <h1>
    <span class="dark-green">When small enterprises choose Gossamer,</span> they don't stay small for long.
  </h1>
  <p>
    We take a partnership role with growing enterprises by helping them evolve
    their processes, and providing highly customized technical solutions that
    take into account their big picture needs.
  </p>
</div><!-- end .masthead -->

<div class="span-15 append-1 content-text"><!-- main-col -->

  <!-- begin item -->
  <a href="/results/sme/flip-media.html"><img class="span-4" src="http://static.gossamer-threads.com/r3/images/logos/logo-flip-150x126.png" width="150" height="126" alt="Flip Media logo" /></a>
  <div class="span-10 last append-bottom-2">
    <h2><a href="/results/sme/flip-media.html">Flip Media</a></h2>
    <p>
      Flip Media is an ad agency that needed a way to streamline the
      communication and mail management of its offices, spanning 9 cities and
      20 different languages. Gossamer provided managed hosting of their e-mail
      through a custom installation of Zimbra, an open-source calendar, e-mail
      and collaboration server that also allows for document storage.
    </p>
    <p class="more"><a href="/results/sme/flip-media.html">Read Case Study for Flip Media&nbsp;<span>&raquo;</span></a></p>
  </div>
  <!-- end item -->

  <!-- begin item -->
  <a href="/results/sme/greatmail.html"><img class="span-4" src="http://static.gossamer-threads.com/r3/images/logos/logo-greatmail-150x126.png" width="150" height="126" alt="Greatmail logo" /></a>
  <div class="span-10 last">
    <h2><a href="/results/sme/greatmail.html">Greatmail</a></h2>
    <p>
      Gossamer Threads' existing hosting client, Greatmail, needed a more robust
      system for reselling Gossamer Mail paid accounts to their own clients.
      GT built a much larger hosting environment (20-25 servers) that
      could scale quickly when Greatmail needed more space for hosting new POP3
      and IMAP email accounts, or for sending out large announcements.
    </p>
    <p class="more"><a href="/results/sme/greatmail.html">Read Case Study for Greatmail&nbsp;<span>&raquo;</span></a></p>
  </div>
  <!-- end item -->

  <!-- begin item -->
  <a href="/results/sme/blue-sky-footage.html"><img class="span-4" src="http://static.gossamer-threads.com/r3/images/logos/logo-bluesky-150x126.png" width="150" height="126" alt="Blue Sky Footage" /></a>
  <div class="span-10 last">
    <h2><a href="/results/sme/blue-sky-footage.html">Blue Sky Footage</a></h2>
    <p>
      Blue Sky Footage approached Gossamer Threads with a desire to create a stock
      video footage website that would offer high-quality video clips shot by
      cinematographers with impressive credentials. Gossamer needed to
      streamline the creation of many formats from one raw source file, as well
      as provide enough storage for the massive inventory of files.
    </p>
    <p class="more"><a href="/results/sme/blue-sky-footage.html">Read the Case Study for Blue Sky Footage&nbsp;<span>&raquo;</span></a></p>
  </div>
  <!-- end item -->


</div><!-- end main-col -->

<div class="span-5 append-3 last"><!-- inner-right-col -->
  <h2>What others say</h2>
  <blockquote>
    <p>
      Gossamer has provided us not only with an extremely reliable hosting
      solution but also with incredible high standards of service, technical
      know-how and advice in putting a hosting farm of 35 servers together that
      maximize the investments of our clients across the Middle East, India
      Europe and Africa.
    </p>
    <div class="pointer"></div>
  </blockquote>
  <p>
    <em>
      – Martin Diessner<br />
      Group CEO - Flip Holding Ltd.
    </em>
  </p>
